</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/86a67b81c2de995bd608d5b2df50cd8cd7d92455" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:1.007ex; height:1.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle c}"=
></span> is given below.
</p><p>Consider the function
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle f(x)=3D{\frac {x^{2}-1}{x-1}}.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>f</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>1</mn>
            </mrow>
            <mrow>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>1</mn>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>.</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle f(x)=3D{\frac=
 {x^{2}-1}{x-1}}.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/ef3ab8444df18b621fd612bf7f1edf8f3e3f3844" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -2.005ex; width:15.386ex; height:5.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle f=
(x)=3D{\frac {x^{2}-1}{x-1}}.}"></span>
</p><p>then <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(1)</span> is not defined (see =
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indeterminate_form" title=3D"Indet=
erminate form">Indeterminate form</a>), yet as <span class=3D"texhtml mvar"=
 style=3D"font-style:italic;">x</span> moves arbitrarily close to 1, <span =
class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(<i>x</i>)</span> correspondingly approaches 2:<s=
up id=3D"cite_ref-14" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.o=
rg/wiki/Limit_(mathematics)#cite_note-14"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</s=
pan>14<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
<table class=3D"wikitable">
<tbody><tr>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(0.9)</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(0.99)</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(0.999)</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(1.0)</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(1.001)</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(1.01)</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(1.1)</span>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml">1.900</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml">1.990</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml">1.999</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml">undefined</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml">2.001</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml">2.010</span></td>
<td><span class=3D"texhtml">2.100</span>
</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>Thus, <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(<i>x</i>)</span> can be made arbi=
trarily close to the limit of 2=E2=80=94just by making <span class=3D"texht=
ml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">x</span> sufficiently close to <span =
class=3D"nowrap"><span class=3D"texhtml">1</span>.</span> In other words,
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle \lim _{x\to 1}{\frac {x^{2}-1}{x-1}}=3D2.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <munder>
          <mo movablelimits=3D"true" form=3D"prefix">lim</mo>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>x</mi>
            <mo stretchy=3D"false">=E2=86=92<!-- =E2=86=92 --></mo>
            <mn>1</mn>
          </mrow>
        </munder>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>1</mn>
            </mrow>
            <mrow>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>1</mn>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>2.</mn>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \lim _{x\to 1=
}{\frac {x^{2}-1}{x-1}}=3D2.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/79d3aa91788da682b1ed6d9e71db8f17ba567a7f" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
