<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Continuous_functions">Conti=
nuous functions</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editse=
ction-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?titl=
e=3DLimit_(mathematics)&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D22" title=3D"Edit s=
ection: Continuous functions"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editse=
ction-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>An important class of functions when considering limits are <a href=3D"h=
ttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Continuous_function" title=3D"Continuous funct=
ion">continuous functions</a>. These are precisely those functions which <i=
